<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="B" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Brevity" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Brevity,</orth> shortness: <cit><quote>imitate the honourabe Romans in b.</quote> <bibl n="shak. 2h4 2.2.135" default="NO" valid="yes">H4B II, 2, 135</bibl></cit>. <emph>the rude b. and discharge of one</emph> (sigh), <bibl n="shak. tro 4.4.43" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. IV, 4, 43</bibl>. <cit><quote>b. is the soul of wit,</quote> <bibl n="shak. ham 2.2.90" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. II, 2, 90</bibl></cit>.
